text: Forges de Lanouée () is a commune in the Morbihan department in Brittany, north-western France. It was established on 1 January 2019 by merger of the former communes of Lanouée (the seat) and Les Forges.Arrêté préfectoral 27 December 2018 ==See also== *Communes of the Morbihan department ==References== Category:Communes of Morbihan
title: Forges de Lanouée
